ction> vnd <instruction>stoz an ain <tool en="rotisserie" commodity="Q22847">spyss</tool></instruction> vnd <instruction>sprens mit <ingredient en="table salt" commodity="Q11254">salcz</ingredient> vnd mit <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffer</ingredient></instruction></alternative> <closer>etc.</closer></div></body></text></TEI>